description:
November 2000, Leeds, Yorkshire. Many teenagers were Christmas shopping in Leeds City Centre, excited about the upcoming holidays. Two friends took a bus to where they lived in the early evening, once they had bought their gifts, but one never made it home.&#13;
&#13;
In this episode of the UK Crime Weekly Podcast we look at what happened on that fateful evening.&#13;
